summary: An extremely big, complete and detailed .INI file for /MyGames/Skyrim/ for tweaking.
descriptionHtml:
___________________________________IMPORTANT________________________________________
EDIT: To have your own settings dumped type in the console: setini <press enter> saveini custom

I was screwing around with the INI files on the Skyrim Console and I got the game to dump this insanely large and complete INI file, with, I believe, every single value in the game (and some that aren\'t in the game such as dragon riding speed, and VATS values), It already comes with a lot of predetermined values, but most of them are somewhat volatile, so I recommend you to not Copypasta.

This was dumped by the game itself, I own nothing, I wrote nothing, I DO NOT take responsibility for whatever insane tweaks, or blatant screwups one may do, and I credit the existance of such file to Bethesda itself.
author: Caassapaba
